<br>
On a side note, SK's feel horrendously underpowered until 60.  Once you get Death Peace (4 second recast FD = yummy), you'll definetely enjoy the class more.<br>
<br>
As far as twinking your enchanter.  I would suggest focusing on +HP and +Mana items.  You'll have to make up your own mind (partially based on race) as far as if you want to focus on INT or CHA after that.  25k can definetely see you through to 46.  Most people starting out in the game don't obtain 25k worth of gear until they are in the 50's.<br>
<br>
Some recommendations I'd make:<br>
<br>
Cloak of Greater Pernicity.  The prices seem to be falling through the floor lately, so you should be able to pick up one cheap.  <br>
<br>
Spider Fur Belt.  Hard to beat this until 51.  I bag my Garish Sash for this when I need the ac/hp to give the group healer(s) time to cover me.<br>
<br>
Earring of the Solstice.  I know the recommended level is 51, but the FT1 on the item starts working at 44 iirc.  Very useful to have hp on your ear slot (along with mana, saves, etc.) so I'd suggest picking up one of these.<br>
<br>
Coldain Skin Gloves and Boots.  These are two fairly cheap (relative to your 25k) upgrades that can last you for quite some time and aren't level restricted.<br>
<br>
If you're lacking in the CHA department, pick up a Bracelet of Beauty for 1-2k.<br>
<br>
Hope that helps to get you started. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=bum3dan>Bum3dan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#330000>(7/28/03 12:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=88.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Help! </span><hr size=1> Ok, that helps. But the thing is i dont want to get SK to 60..lol i hate leveling and all i do is naggy/vox pick up raids and would enchanter be funner for that? I mean i just want to level something up thats fun while leveling and fun/ can make money in long end..btw ive had ALOT of level 65 characters and have played almost every class except ench,mage,shaman...1 more thing cloak of greater pern. is still 15k on my server.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
